{"tid":1797288,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"銅鑼灣劫案 賊持刀槍搶掠","createTime":"2019-12-25T09:54:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T10:09:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f9510dab33363f48a4c5d6c6a3f2c4936d907aa4","tid":1797288,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T09:54:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191224/DPN4ISOK4ZDOSFHUSNN26AVYHQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191224%2FDPN4ISOK4ZDOSFHUSNN26AVYHQ%2F&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFMyzqlNZT0%2FxJNtMGMfIkD0%3D&h=15c9fcd6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191224%2FDPN4ISOK4ZDOSFHUSNN26AVYHQ%2F&h=6b099c7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191224/DPN4ISOK4ZDOSFHUSNN26AVYHQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n銅鑼灣劫案 賊持刀槍搶掠<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】前晚遭賊人扑爆櫥窗玻璃掠走總值60萬元手錶的銅鑼灣廣場「28watches」錶行，因要進行維修用木板圍封暫停營業，東主估計要逾十天始能重新開店，並希望警方盡快捉到賊人。錶行閉路電視片段顯示，三賊行劫時，其中一名手持刀槍賊人，不停用槍指向四周阻嚇其他人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191224/large/1577117630_edb3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191224%2Flarge%2F1577117630_edb3.jpg&h=8c36644c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n遇劫錶行門口用圍板封鎖，等候重新安裝飾櫃玻璃。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCCTV拍下過程<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：拋「學術研究」歸咎市民<br />\n<br />\n「28watches」東主Leon表示，由於店舖玻璃被賊人打碎，需要重新預訂玻璃，估計要用十天至兩星期時間修復店舖，其後才能重新開店營業。錶行附近店舖照常營業，商場保安亦有加強巡邏，但其他店舖對警方減少巡邏不願置評。<br />\n<br />\n案發前晚近7時，三賊闖入銅鑼灣廣場行劫「28watches」錶行，掠走12隻手錶，錶行閉路電視拍攝到行劫過程。據錄影片段顯示，店內當時至少有一名職員，三名賊人其中一人雙手分持仿製槍及利刀在場把風，另兩賊則不斷用硬物敲擊大門櫥窗玻璃，後見強化玻璃無法擊碎，賊人瘋狂拉扯損毀的櫥窗，再從旁邊拉起的空位，伸手入內搶掠；其間，持刀槍賊人不停用槍指向四周指嚇，得手後挾贓逃去。<br />\n<br />\n■記者翁鈺輝"},{"pid":"13fd1dc607b03768c6cc469ebc0cc2b80bfea273","tid":1797288,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T09:55:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">無忘承諾 並肩同行<br />\n民陣元誕大遊行</span><br />\n日期 : 1月1日 (三)<br />\n時間：14:00<br />\n地點：維園中央草坪 ==&gt; 遮打道行人專用區"},{"pid":"ee7ade5c11b75eb4068377ac93a93667b3fa64df","tid":1797288,"uid":48315,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T09:58:00.000Z","msg":"真開心 頭幾單做大個瞻 依家日日都有<br />\n反正就算現場拉唔到 事後又掛住拉示威者<br />\n啲金鋪錶鋪人人自危"},{"pid":"a2919b7e00112ea88ae9f4232ad72d2eb0b4e29d","tid":1797288,"uid":37058,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ee7ade5c11b75eb4068377ac93a93667b3fa64df","tid":1797288,"uid":48315,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T09:58:00.000Z","msg":"真開心 頭幾單做大個瞻 依家日日都有<br />\n反正就算現場拉唔到 事後又掛住拉示威者<br />\n啲金鋪錶鋪人人自危"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T10:01:16.000Z","msg":"話唔係同狗夾埋都無人信啦"},{"pid":"05517360bc9c4bdc334c23a2fb3779d51fa36c60","tid":1797288,"uid":6363,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a2919b7e00112ea88ae9f4232ad72d2eb0b4e29d","tid":1797288,"uid":37058,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ee7ade5c11b75eb4068377ac93a93667b3fa64df","tid":1797288,"uid":48315,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T09:58:00.000Z","msg":"真開心 頭幾單做大個瞻 依家日日都有<br />\n反正就算現場拉唔到 事後又掛住拉示威者<br />\n啲金鋪錶鋪人人自危"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T10:01:16.000Z","msg":"話唔係同狗夾埋都無人信啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T10:04:55.000Z","msg":"煲大d狗狗寧願拉人貼連豬都唔捉賊。<br />\n唔好畀狗把治安差嘅責任推落示威活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6759133eb8ce201f289fde171ea2304a5a4ebe50","tid":1797288,"uid":221055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T10:04:58.000Z","msg":"點解未捉到人都知係仿製槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02182a2cdd284cfe114fb88eb4f32a3f03fe090f","tid":1797288,"uid":19476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a2919b7e00112ea88ae9f4232ad72d2eb0b4e29d","tid":1797288,"uid":37058,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ee7ade5c11b75eb4068377ac93a93667b3fa64df","tid":1797288,"uid":48315,"